<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊正在修理鸡圈的铁丝网。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！” 她满意地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她锁上鸡圈门，朝房子走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，凉凉、湿湿的东西掉在了她的脸上。是雪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！凯蒂！下雪了！” 乔伊边喊边跑进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于下雪了。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和奥利维亚坐在桌前，正喝着第二杯热可可。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我非常喜欢雪。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊过来搂住了她的朋友，“谢谢你能来。很感谢你帮了我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是朋友的意义。” 奥利维亚笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也帮忙了。” 凯蒂一边说，一边戳她姐姐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，赶紧完成你的作业吧。我们明天得玩儿雪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊笑了，“别担心，我会写完的。我保证！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚看着窗外，她睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要打电话叫我妈妈来接我，雪下得太大了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚走后，双胞胎坐在客厅里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊在写她的作业，凯蒂在翻看杂志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面的一切都被白色的雪覆盖了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，凯蒂叹了口气。“我觉得好无聊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来接！” 凯蒂跑向电话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在厨房里的妈妈看了看钟表，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该是爸爸和爷爷，” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们很快就会回来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，爸爸！” 凯蒂接起电话说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的雪也下得很大......哦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂的声音变低了，“哦，不，好吧......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂把电话递给了妈妈，“爸爸要跟您说话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈接过电话后，凯蒂马上回去找乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸和爷爷被困住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高速公路因为大雪封闭了！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不，他们该怎么办呢？” 乔伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说会去其他城市的旅馆。” 妈妈说完，也坐到了孩子们边上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，明天早上公路就会被打扫干净的。” 妈妈补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这意味着我们还能再在一起度过一个晚上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有女孩子们! ” 乔伊笑着对妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一边看电影一边吃爆米花！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定会很有意思的！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 妈妈说，“不过，你们俩都有作业要做，不是吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有。” 凯蒂说，“我的发表写完了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊犹豫了一下，“我还有事情要做，可是......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在换作是哈丽特·塔布曼，你觉得她会怎么做呢？” 妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，乔伊想起了一个有关哈丽特·塔布曼的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她为了自由逃跑时，一路从马里兰走到了宾夕法尼亚，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那大概有两百公里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没有一句抱怨，一直不停地走，也没有放弃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊叹了口气。“好吧，妈妈，我继续写我的发表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，我们在厨房烤布朗尼，怎么样？” 妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂点了点头，跟着妈妈走出了客厅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得让乔伊一个人待着。” 妈妈小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样，她才能完成她的作业。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。” 凯蒂也小声说。她尽量保持安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看看能不能找到爷爷的布朗尼做法。” 妈妈小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小时过去了，乔伊还在客厅里写作业。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她闻到了一股烧焦了的味道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！” 凯蒂喊了一声。她端来了一大盘布朗尼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，嘘！” 妈妈提醒她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀。” 凯蒂咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！” 她小声说，“烤糊的布朗尼可以帮你集中注意力！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊咯咯地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经记不起来凯蒂上一次烤的是什么了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哦，不是！是记不起来凯蒂为她烤的是什么了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 她说，“有你真好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂又向乔伊做了一个  “双胞胎” 的手势。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈把手放到了乔伊的肩膀上，“晚安，宝贝，别做得太晚了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，妈妈。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她为了完成发表又写了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>